            "content": "<p>Unlike mass-produced saunas, every unit is built with thick 2×6 tongue-and-groove wall panels for superior insulation, tempered glass doors, and a roof designed to handle heavy snow loads.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What's Included",
